{
    "1216:0": "XXIII",
    "1216:1": "śakraparivarto nāma trayoviṃśatitamaḥ|",
    "1216:2": "tena khalu punarityādi evaṃ śikṣamāṇaṃ cetyataḥ prāk|",
    "1216:3": "sadevamānuṣāsuraṃ lokaṃ sarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhayānikānanupāyakuśalāṃśca bodhisattvo'bhibhavati|",
    "1216:4": "teṣāṃ cānabhibhūto bhavatīti pañcamī vivṛddhiḥ||",
    "1216:5": "evaṃ śikṣamāṇaṃ cetyādi āparivartāntāt|",
    "1216:6": "catvāro lokapālāḥ śakrastadanye ca devāstamupasaṃkramiṣyantītyādibhiranuśaṃsaiḥ ṣaṣṭhī||",
    "1216:7": "śakreṇoktaḥ parivartaḥ śakraparivartaḥ||",
    "1216:8": "āryāṣṭasāhasrikāyāḥ prajñāpāramitāyāḥ sāratamānāmni pañjikāyāṃ ratnākaraśāntiviracitāyāṃ trayoviṃśatitamaḥ parivartaḥ||"
}